<plot>Dis Için Göz Çikartmak (An Eye for a Tooth) tells the story of two families interwoven over several generations. Most family members place honor above everything, while a courageous few believe it is wiser to question tradition. Efkan, a successful businessman living in London, finds his comfortable life in turmoil when he finds out that he is the target of a killer. An unknown assassin from his native Turkey wants to kill him to satisfy a generation-old blood feud. Charlotte, Efkan's wife, this code of revenge, and fears that their 5-year-old son could become a victim of this ancient tradition.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?037107</url></doc>
